# Deny by default -- this repo tracks only the compiler sources, the
# Makefile, and the testsuite. Everything else in this working directory
# (scratch .t files, one-off refactor scripts, backups, compiled binaries,
# stdlib/docs/tools/examples not yet ready to publish) is intentionally
# left untracked rather than deleted.
*

!.gitignore

!*.c
!*.h
!Makefile
!test.sh

!testsuite/
!testsuite/**

!README.md
!.gitattributes
!docs/
!docs/REFERENCE.md

!.github/
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/ci.yml

# Scratch/debug one-off tools at root -- not part of the real compiler build
# (see Makefile's SRC list for what actually is).
aot_shim.c
poc_main.c
print_ast_enums.c
print_ast_return.c
print_jit.c
runner.c
test_offset.c
